These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, tea
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, dutch
1. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
2. the dutch is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | tea  | juice |
| Nationality       | thai | dutch |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, march
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
2. the person drinking water is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | water |
| Birthday      | march     | november  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, rose
There are 2 different nationalities: french, nigerian
1. the french is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
2. the french is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Flower   | daffodil | rose  |
| Nationality   | french | nigerian |

 #################################

 
