There are 2 different nationalities: american, australian
1. the australian is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Sport   | snowboarding    | ice-hockey    |
| Nationality   | american | australian |

