.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-8::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, woodworking
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, water-polo
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | singing |
| Sport     | snowboarding        | water-polo |

