1. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Birthday         | december | july |
| Music-Genre   | r&b     | d&b     |

